{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.1","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 7:1","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.006.038,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.007.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Construction du palais de Salomon<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-12: cf. 2 Ch 8:1, 11; 9:17-20. Ec 2:4.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.7.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>Salomon b\u00e2tit encore sa maison, ce qui dura treize ans jusqu\u2019\u00e0 ce qu\u2019il l\u2019e\u00fbt enti\u00e8rement achev\u00e9e.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7","name":"1 Rois 7","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.2","name":"1 Rois 7:2","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.38","name":"1 Rois 6:38","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.38"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.2","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 7:2","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.007.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.007.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.7.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>Il construisit d\u2019abord la maison de la for\u00eat du Liban, longue de cent coud\u00e9es, large de cinquante coud\u00e9es, et haute de trente coud\u00e9es. Elle reposait sur quatre rang\u00e9es de colonnes de c\u00e8dre, et il y avait des poutres de c\u00e8dre sur les colonnes.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7","name":"1 Rois 7","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.3","name":"1 Rois 7:3","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.1","name":"1 Rois 7:1","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.3","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 7:3","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.007.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.007.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.7.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>On couvrit de c\u00e8dre les chambres qui portaient sur les colonnes et qui \u00e9taient au nombre de quarante-cinq, quinze par \u00e9tage.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7","name":"1 Rois 7","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.4","name":"1 Rois 7:4","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.2","name":"1 Rois 7:2","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.4","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 7:4","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.007.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.007.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.7.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>Il y avait trois \u00e9tages, \u00e0 chacun desquels se trouvaient des fen\u00eatres les unes vis-\u00e0-vis des autres.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7","name":"1 Rois 7","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.5","name":"1 Rois 7:5","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.3","name":"1 Rois 7:3","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.5","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 7:5","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.007.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.007.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.7.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>Toutes les portes et tous les poteaux \u00e9taient form\u00e9s de poutres en carr\u00e9; et, \u00e0 chacun des trois \u00e9tages, les ouvertures \u00e9taient les unes vis-\u00e0-vis des autres.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7","name":"1 Rois 7","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.6","name":"1 Rois 7:6","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.4","name":"1 Rois 7:4","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.6","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 7:6","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.007.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.007.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.7.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>Il fit le portique des colonnes, long de cinquante coud\u00e9es et large de trente coud\u00e9es, et un autre portique en avant avec des colonnes et des degr\u00e9s sur leur front.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7","name":"1 Rois 7","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.7","name":"1 Rois 7:7","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.5","name":"1 Rois 7:5","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.7","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 7:7","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.007.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.007.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.7.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>Il fit le portique du tr\u00f4ne, o\u00f9 il rendait la justice, le portique du jugement; et il le couvrit de c\u00e8dre, depuis le sol jusqu\u2019au plafond.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7","name":"1 Rois 7","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.8","name":"1 Rois 7:8","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.6","name":"1 Rois 7:6","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.8","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 7:8","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.007.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.007.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.7.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Sa maison d\u2019habitation fut construite de la m\u00eame mani\u00e8re, dans une autre cour, derri\u00e8re le portique. Et il fit une maison du m\u00eame genre que ce portique pour la fille de Pharaon, qu\u2019il avait prise pour femme.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7","name":"1 Rois 7","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.9","name":"1 Rois 7:9","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.7","name":"1 Rois 7:7","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.9","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 7:9","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.007.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.007.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.7.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>Pour toutes ces constructions on employa de magnifiques pierres, taill\u00e9es d\u2019apr\u00e8s des mesures, sci\u00e9es avec la scie, int\u00e9rieurement et ext\u00e9rieurement, et cela depuis les fondements jusqu\u2019aux corniches, et en dehors jusqu\u2019\u00e0 la grande cour.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7","name":"1 Rois 7","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.10","name":"1 Rois 7:10","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.8","name":"1 Rois 7:8","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.10","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 7:10","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.007.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.007.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.7.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>Les fondements \u00e9taient en pierres magnifiques et de grande dimension, en pierres de dix coud\u00e9es et en pierres de huit coud\u00e9es.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7","name":"1 Rois 7","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.11","name":"1 Rois 7:11","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.9","name":"1 Rois 7:9","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.11","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 7:11","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.007.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.007.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.7.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Au-dessus il y avait encore de magnifiques pierres, taill\u00e9es d\u2019apr\u00e8s des mesures, et du bois de c\u00e8dre.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7","name":"1 Rois 7","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.12","name":"1 Rois 7:12","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.10","name":"1 Rois 7:10","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.12","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 7:12","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.007.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.007.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.7.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>La grande cour avait dans tout son circuit trois rang\u00e9es de pierres de taille et une rang\u00e9e de poutres de c\u00e8dre, comme le parvis int\u00e9rieur de la maison de l\u2019\u00c9ternel, et comme le portique de la maison.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7","name":"1 Rois 7","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.13","name":"1 Rois 7:13","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.11","name":"1 Rois 7:11","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.13","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 7:13","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.007.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.007.014,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Les deux colonnes d\u2019airain, la mer d\u2019airain, les bassins, et les divers ustensiles pour le temple<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 13-22: cf. 2 Ch 2:12-14; 3:15-17.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.7.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>Le roi Salomon fit venir de Tyr Hiram,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7","name":"1 Rois 7","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.14","name":"1 Rois 7:14","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.12","name":"1 Rois 7:12","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.14","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 7:14","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.007.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.007.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.7.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>fils d\u2019une veuve de la tribu de Nephthali, et d\u2019un p\u00e8re Tyrien, qui travaillait sur l\u2019airain. Hiram \u00e9tait rempli de sagesse, d\u2019intelligence, et de savoir pour faire toutes sortes d\u2019ouvrages d\u2019airain. Il arriva aupr\u00e8s du roi Salomon, et il ex\u00e9cuta tous ses ouvrages.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7","name":"1 Rois 7","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.15","name":"1 Rois 7:15","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.13","name":"1 Rois 7:13","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.15","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 7:15","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.007.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.007.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.7.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>Il fit les deux colonnes d\u2019airain. La premi\u00e8re avait dix-huit coud\u00e9es de hauteur, et un fil de douze coud\u00e9es mesurait la circonf\u00e9rence de la seconde.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7","name":"1 Rois 7","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.16","name":"1 Rois 7:16","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.14","name":"1 Rois 7:14","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.16","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 7:16","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.007.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.007.017,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.7.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>Il fondit deux chapiteaux d\u2019airain, pour mettre sur les sommets des colonnes; le premier avait cinq coud\u00e9es de hauteur, et le second avait cinq coud\u00e9es de hauteur.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7","name":"1 Rois 7","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.17","name":"1 Rois 7:17","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.15","name":"1 Rois 7:15","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.17","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 7:17","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.007.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.007.018,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.7.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>Il fit des treillis en forme de r\u00e9seaux, des festons fa\u00e7onn\u00e9s en cha\u00eenettes, pour les chapiteaux qui \u00e9taient sur le sommet des colonnes, sept pour le premier chapiteau, et sept pour le second chapiteau.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7","name":"1 Rois 7","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.18","name":"1 Rois 7:18","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.18"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.16","name":"1 Rois 7:16","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"18","lastverse":"18","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.18","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.18","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 7:18","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.007.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.007.019,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.7.18\" class=\"v\">18<\/sup>Il fit deux rangs de grenades autour de l\u2019un des treillis, pour couvrir le chapiteau qui \u00e9tait sur le sommet d\u2019une des colonnes; il fit de m\u00eame pour le second chapiteau.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7","name":"1 Rois 7","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.19","name":"1 Rois 7:19","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.19"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.17","name":"1 Rois 7:17","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"19","lastverse":"19","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.19","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.19","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 7:19","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.007.018,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.007.020,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.7.19\" class=\"v\">19<\/sup>Les chapiteaux qui \u00e9taient sur le sommet des colonnes, dans le portique, figuraient des lis et avaient quatre coud\u00e9es.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7","name":"1 Rois 7","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.20","name":"1 Rois 7:20","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.20"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.18","name":"1 Rois 7:18","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.18"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"20","lastverse":"20","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.20","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.20","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 7:20","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.007.019,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.007.021,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.7.20\" class=\"v\">20<\/sup>Les chapiteaux plac\u00e9s sur les deux colonnes \u00e9taient entour\u00e9s de deux cents grenades, en haut, pr\u00e8s du renflement qui \u00e9tait au-del\u00e0 du treillis; il y avait aussi deux cents grenades rang\u00e9es autour du second chapiteau.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7","name":"1 Rois 7","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.21","name":"1 Rois 7:21","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.21"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.19","name":"1 Rois 7:19","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.19"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"21","lastverse":"21","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.21","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.21","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 7:21","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.007.020,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.007.022,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.7.21\" class=\"v\">21<\/sup>Il dressa les colonnes dans le portique du temple; il dressa la colonne de droite, et la nomma Jakin; puis il dressa la colonne de gauche, et la nomma Boaz.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7","name":"1 Rois 7","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.22","name":"1 Rois 7:22","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.22"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.20","name":"1 Rois 7:20","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.20"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"22","lastverse":"22","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.22","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.22","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 7:22","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.007.021,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.007.023,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.7.22\" class=\"v\">22<\/sup>Il y avait sur le sommet des colonnes un travail figurant des lis. Ainsi fut achev\u00e9 l\u2019ouvrage des colonnes.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7","name":"1 Rois 7","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.23","name":"1 Rois 7:23","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.23"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.21","name":"1 Rois 7:21","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.21"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"23","lastverse":"23","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.23","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.23","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 7:23","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.007.022,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.007.024,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 23-40: cf. 2 Ch 4:1-6. Ex 30:17-21.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.7.23\" class=\"v\">23<\/sup>\n    Il fit la mer de fonte. Elle avait dix coud\u00e9es d\u2019un bord \u00e0 l\u2019autre, une forme enti\u00e8rement ronde, cinq coud\u00e9es de hauteur, et une circonf\u00e9rence que mesurait un cordon de trente coud\u00e9es.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7","name":"1 Rois 7","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.24","name":"1 Rois 7:24","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.24"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.22","name":"1 Rois 7:22","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.22"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"24","lastverse":"24","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.24","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.24","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 7:24","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.007.023,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.007.025,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.7.24\" class=\"v\">24<\/sup>Des coloquintes l\u2019entouraient au-dessous de son bord, dix par coud\u00e9e, faisant tout le tour de la mer; les coloquintes, dispos\u00e9es sur deux rangs, \u00e9taient fondues avec elle en une seule pi\u00e8ce.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7","name":"1 Rois 7","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.25","name":"1 Rois 7:25","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.25"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.23","name":"1 Rois 7:23","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.23"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"25","lastverse":"25","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.25","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.25","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 7:25","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.007.024,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.007.026,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.7.25\" class=\"v\">25<\/sup>Elle \u00e9tait pos\u00e9e sur douze b\u0153ufs, dont trois tourn\u00e9s vers le nord, trois tourn\u00e9s vers l\u2019occident, trois tourn\u00e9s vers le midi, et trois tourn\u00e9s vers l\u2019orient; la mer \u00e9tait sur eux, et toute la partie post\u00e9rieure de leur corps \u00e9tait en dedans.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7","name":"1 Rois 7","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.26","name":"1 Rois 7:26","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.26"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.24","name":"1 Rois 7:24","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.24"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"26","lastverse":"26","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.26","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.26","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 7:26","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.007.025,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.007.027,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.7.26\" class=\"v\">26<\/sup>Son \u00e9paisseur \u00e9tait d\u2019un palme; et son bord, semblable au bord d\u2019une coupe, \u00e9tait fa\u00e7onn\u00e9 en fleur de lis. Elle contenait deux mille baths.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7","name":"1 Rois 7","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.27","name":"1 Rois 7:27","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.27"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.25","name":"1 Rois 7:25","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.25"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"27","lastverse":"27","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.27","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.27","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 7:27","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.007.026,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.007.028,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.7.27\" class=\"v\">27<\/sup>Il fit les dix bases d\u2019airain. Chacune avait quatre coud\u00e9es de longueur, quatre coud\u00e9es de largeur, et trois coud\u00e9es de hauteur.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7","name":"1 Rois 7","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.28","name":"1 Rois 7:28","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.28"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.26","name":"1 Rois 7:26","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.26"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"28","lastverse":"28","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.28","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.28","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 7:28","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.007.027,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.007.029,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.7.28\" class=\"v\">28<\/sup>Voici en quoi consistaient ces bases. Elles \u00e9taient form\u00e9es de panneaux, li\u00e9s aux coins par des montants.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7","name":"1 Rois 7","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.29","name":"1 Rois 7:29","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.29"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.27","name":"1 Rois 7:27","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.27"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"29","lastverse":"29","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.29","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.29","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 7:29","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.007.028,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.007.030,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.7.29\" class=\"v\">29<\/sup>Sur les panneaux qui \u00e9taient entre les montants il y avait des lions, des b\u0153ufs et des ch\u00e9rubins; et sur les montants, au-dessus comme au-dessous des lions et des b\u0153ufs, il y avait des ornements qui pendaient en festons.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7","name":"1 Rois 7","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.30","name":"1 Rois 7:30","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.30"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.28","name":"1 Rois 7:28","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.28"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"30","lastverse":"30","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.30","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.30","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 7:30","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.007.029,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.007.031,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.7.30\" class=\"v\">30<\/sup>Chaque base avait quatre roues d\u2019airain avec des essieux d\u2019airain; et aux quatre angles \u00e9taient des consoles de fonte, au-dessous du bassin, et au-del\u00e0 des festons.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7","name":"1 Rois 7","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.31","name":"1 Rois 7:31","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.31"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.29","name":"1 Rois 7:29","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.29"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"31","lastverse":"31","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.31","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.31","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 7:31","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.007.030,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.007.032,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.7.31\" class=\"v\">31<\/sup>Le couronnement de la base offrait \u00e0 son int\u00e9rieur une ouverture avec un prolongement d\u2019une coud\u00e9e vers le haut; cette ouverture \u00e9tait ronde, comme pour les ouvrages de ce genre, et elle avait une coud\u00e9e et demie de largeur; il s\u2019y trouvait aussi des sculptures. Les panneaux \u00e9taient carr\u00e9s, et non arrondis.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7","name":"1 Rois 7","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.32","name":"1 Rois 7:32","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.32"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.30","name":"1 Rois 7:30","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.30"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"32","lastverse":"32","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.32","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.32","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 7:32","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.007.031,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.007.033,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.7.32\" class=\"v\">32<\/sup>Les quatre roues \u00e9taient sous les panneaux, et les essieux des roues fix\u00e9s \u00e0 la base; chacune avait une coud\u00e9e et demie de hauteur.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7","name":"1 Rois 7","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.33","name":"1 Rois 7:33","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.33"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.31","name":"1 Rois 7:31","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.31"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"33","lastverse":"33","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.33","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.33","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 7:33","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.007.032,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.007.034,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.7.33\" class=\"v\">33<\/sup>Les roues \u00e9taient faites comme celles d\u2019un char. Leurs essieux, leurs jantes, leurs rais et leurs moyeux, tout \u00e9tait de fonte.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7","name":"1 Rois 7","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.34","name":"1 Rois 7:34","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.34"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.32","name":"1 Rois 7:32","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.32"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"34","lastverse":"34","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.34","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.34","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 7:34","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.007.033,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.007.035,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.7.34\" class=\"v\">34<\/sup>Il y avait aux quatre angles de chaque base quatre consoles d\u2019une m\u00eame pi\u00e8ce que la base.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7","name":"1 Rois 7","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.35","name":"1 Rois 7:35","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.35"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.33","name":"1 Rois 7:33","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.33"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"35","lastverse":"35","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.35","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.35","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 7:35","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.007.034,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.007.036,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.7.35\" class=\"v\">35<\/sup>La partie sup\u00e9rieure de la base se terminait par un cercle d\u2019une demi-coud\u00e9e de hauteur, et elle avait ses appuis et ses panneaux de la m\u00eame pi\u00e8ce.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7","name":"1 Rois 7","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.36","name":"1 Rois 7:36","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.36"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.34","name":"1 Rois 7:34","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.34"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"36","lastverse":"36","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.36","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.36","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 7:36","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.007.035,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.007.037,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.7.36\" class=\"v\">36<\/sup>Il grava sur les plaques des appuis, et sur les panneaux, des ch\u00e9rubins, des lions et des palmes, selon les espaces libres, et des guirlandes tout autour.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7","name":"1 Rois 7","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.37","name":"1 Rois 7:37","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.37"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.35","name":"1 Rois 7:35","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.35"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"37","lastverse":"37","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.37","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.37","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 7:37","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.007.036,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.007.038,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.7.37\" class=\"v\">37<\/sup>C\u2019est ainsi qu\u2019il fit les dix bases: la fonte, la mesure et la forme \u00e9taient les m\u00eames pour toutes.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7","name":"1 Rois 7","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.38","name":"1 Rois 7:38","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.38"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.36","name":"1 Rois 7:36","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.36"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"38","lastverse":"38","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.38","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.38","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 7:38","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.007.037,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.007.039,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.7.38\" class=\"v\">38<\/sup>Il fit dix bassins d\u2019airain. Chaque bassin contenait quarante baths, chaque bassin avait quatre coud\u00e9es, chaque bassin \u00e9tait sur l\u2019une des dix bases.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7","name":"1 Rois 7","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.39","name":"1 Rois 7:39","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.39"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.37","name":"1 Rois 7:37","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.37"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"39","lastverse":"39","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.39","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.39","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 7:39","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.007.038,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.007.040,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.7.39\" class=\"v\">39<\/sup>Il pla\u00e7a cinq bases sur le c\u00f4t\u00e9 droit de la maison, et cinq bases sur le c\u00f4t\u00e9 gauche de la maison; et il pla\u00e7a la mer du c\u00f4t\u00e9 droit de la maison, au sud-est.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7","name":"1 Rois 7","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.40","name":"1 Rois 7:40","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.40"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.38","name":"1 Rois 7:38","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.38"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"40","lastverse":"40","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.40","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.40","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 7:40","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.007.039,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.007.041,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.7.40\" class=\"v\">40<\/sup>Hiram fit les cendriers, les pelles et les coupes. Ainsi Hiram acheva tout l\u2019ouvrage que le roi Salomon lui fit faire pour la maison de l\u2019\u00c9ternel;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7","name":"1 Rois 7","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.41","name":"1 Rois 7:41","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.41"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.39","name":"1 Rois 7:39","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.39"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"41","lastverse":"41","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.41","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.41","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 7:41","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.007.040,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.007.042,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 41-51: cf. (2 Ch 4:7-22; 5:1. Ex 37:10, etc.)<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.7.41\" class=\"v\">41<\/sup>deux colonnes, avec les deux chapiteaux et leurs bourrelets sur le sommet des colonnes; les deux treillis, pour couvrir les deux bourrelets des chapiteaux sur le sommet des colonnes;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7","name":"1 Rois 7","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.42","name":"1 Rois 7:42","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.42"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.40","name":"1 Rois 7:40","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.40"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"42","lastverse":"42","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.42","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.42","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 7:42","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.007.041,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.007.043,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.7.42\" class=\"v\">42<\/sup>les quatre cents grenades pour les deux treillis, deux rang\u00e9es de grenades par treillis, pour couvrir les deux bourrelets des chapiteaux sur le sommet des colonnes;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7","name":"1 Rois 7","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.43","name":"1 Rois 7:43","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.43"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.41","name":"1 Rois 7:41","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.41"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"43","lastverse":"43","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.43","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.43","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 7:43","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.007.042,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.007.044,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.7.43\" class=\"v\">43<\/sup>les dix bases, et les dix bassins sur les bases;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7","name":"1 Rois 7","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.44","name":"1 Rois 7:44","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.44"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.42","name":"1 Rois 7:42","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.42"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"44","lastverse":"44","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.44","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.44","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 7:44","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.007.043,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.007.045,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.7.44\" class=\"v\">44<\/sup>la mer, et les douze b\u0153ufs sous la mer;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7","name":"1 Rois 7","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.45","name":"1 Rois 7:45","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.45"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.43","name":"1 Rois 7:43","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.43"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"45","lastverse":"45","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.45","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.45","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 7:45","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.007.044,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.007.046,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.7.45\" class=\"v\">45<\/sup>les cendriers, les pelles et les coupes. Tous ces ustensiles que le roi Salomon fit faire \u00e0 Hiram pour la maison de l\u2019\u00c9ternel \u00e9taient d\u2019airain poli.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7","name":"1 Rois 7","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.46","name":"1 Rois 7:46","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.46"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.44","name":"1 Rois 7:44","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.44"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"46","lastverse":"46","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.46","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.46","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 7:46","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.007.045,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.007.047,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.7.46\" class=\"v\">46<\/sup>Le roi les fit fondre dans la plaine du Jourdain dans un sol argileux, entre Succoth et Tsarthan.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7","name":"1 Rois 7","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.47","name":"1 Rois 7:47","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.47"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.45","name":"1 Rois 7:45","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.45"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"47","lastverse":"47","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.47","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.47","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 7:47","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.007.046,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.007.048,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.7.47\" class=\"v\">47<\/sup>Salomon laissa tous ces ustensiles sans v\u00e9rifier le poids de l\u2019airain, parce qu\u2019ils \u00e9taient en tr\u00e8s grande quantit\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7","name":"1 Rois 7","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.48","name":"1 Rois 7:48","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.48"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.46","name":"1 Rois 7:46","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.46"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"48","lastverse":"48","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.48","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.48","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 7:48","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.007.047,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.007.049,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.7.48\" class=\"v\">48<\/sup>Salomon fit encore tous les autres ustensiles pour la maison de l\u2019\u00c9ternel: l\u2019autel d\u2019or; la table d\u2019or, sur laquelle on mettait les pains de proposition;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7","name":"1 Rois 7","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.49","name":"1 Rois 7:49","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.49"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.47","name":"1 Rois 7:47","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.47"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"49","lastverse":"49","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.49","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.49","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 7:49","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.007.048,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.007.050,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.7.49\" class=\"v\">49<\/sup>les chandeliers d\u2019or pur, cinq \u00e0 droite et cinq \u00e0 gauche, devant le sanctuaire, avec les fleurs, les lampes et les mouchettes d\u2019or;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7","name":"1 Rois 7","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.50","name":"1 Rois 7:50","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.50"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.48","name":"1 Rois 7:48","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.48"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"50","lastverse":"50","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.50","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.50","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 7:50","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.007.049,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.007.051,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.7.50\" class=\"v\">50<\/sup>les bassins, les couteaux, les coupes, les tasses et les brasiers d\u2019or pur; et les gonds d\u2019or pour la porte de l\u2019int\u00e9rieur de la maison \u00e0 l\u2019entr\u00e9e du lieu tr\u00e8s saint, et pour la porte de la maison \u00e0 l\u2019entr\u00e9e du temple.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7","name":"1 Rois 7","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.51","name":"1 Rois 7:51","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.51"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.49","name":"1 Rois 7:49","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.49"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"51","lastverse":"51","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.51","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.51","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 7:51","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.007.050,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.008.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.7.51\" class=\"v\">51<\/sup>Ainsi fut achev\u00e9 tout l\u2019ouvrage que le roi Salomon fit pour la maison de l\u2019\u00c9ternel. Puis il apporta l\u2019argent, l\u2019or et les ustensiles, que David, son p\u00e8re, avait consacr\u00e9s, et il les mit dans les tr\u00e9sors de la maison de l\u2019\u00c9ternel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7","name":"1 Rois 7","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.8.1","name":"1 Rois 8:1","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.8.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.50","name":"1 Rois 7:50","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.50"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fc509e0b5.16739129');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fc509e0b5.16739129\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fc509e0b5.16739129","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81fc509e0b5.16739129'); }","fums_noscript":"<img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfr